    "role": "Credibility assessment team",
    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "All seven assessed credibility factors meet or exceed required levels for MRL 2. Six factors are appropriately not assessed at MRL 2. The CFD model demonstrates sufficient credibility to support the regulatory decision regarding worst-case hemolysis operating conditions for the Class II CPB device. Uncertainty quantification via comprehensive Monte Carlo analysis confirmed that the RH < 1 acceptance criterion is satisfied at the 95th percentile across all five operating points, supporting an Accepted decision.",
